    '{"fuel_type":"combination","template_version":"1.0","pair_key":"jeuveau__rha_redensity","product_a":"Jeuveau","product_b":"RHA Redensity","patient_facing_name":"Relax & Refine","one_line_positioning":"Jeuveau addresses expression lines in the upper face while RHA Redensity refines the fine lines around the mouth that constant movement creates.","package_goal":"Address upper-face expression lines and perioral fine line refinement","ideal_candidate":"Patient experiencing both upper-face dynamic wrinkles and perioral fine lines (lip lines, lines from constant mouth movement); patient seeking comprehensive upper- and lower-face refinement.","not_ideal_candidate":"Patient with single isolated concern; patients with neurotoxin or HA contraindications.","concern_tags":["dynamic wrinkles","frown lines","crow''s feet","perioral lines","lip lines","fine lines","facial aging"],"why_together":"Jeuveau relaxes upper-face expression muscles; RHA Redensity uses resilient HA designed for the perioral zone — an area of constant movement where traditional fillers may not perform well. Different zones, different mechanisms, different product categories.","A_solves":"Relaxes muscles causing dynamic expression lines in the upper face (frown lines, crow''s feet, forehead lines)","A_does_not_solve":"Cannot restore lost volume or refine perioral fine lines","B_adds":"Resilient HA refinement for perioral fine lines in areas of constant movement; finishing-filler function for fine detail after broader structural concerns are addressed","clinical_rationale":"Jeuveau (prabotulinumtoxinA-xvfs) is an aesthetics-only neurotoxin with Hi-Pure technology, addressing upper-face dynamic wrinkles. RHA Redensity uses resilient HA technology specifically designed for perioral fine lines and dynamic areas — it is a finishing filler that refines fine lines in areas of constant movement where traditional fillers may not perform as well. The combination addresses upper-face expression lines (Jeuveau) alongside perioral fine line refinement (RHA Redensity). Jeuveau has limited product-specific published evidence. This is a cross-ecosystem pairing (Evolus + Revance). Jeuveau maintenance: every 3-4 months.","patient_education_summary":"Jeuveau is a wrinkle relaxer designed specifically for cosmetic use — it relaxes the muscles that create expression lines like frown lines and crow''s feet. The fine lines around your mouth are a different type of concern. That area is constantly moving — talking, eating, smiling — and those lines develop from years of that movement combined with skin changes over time. RHA Redensity is a specialized filler designed for exactly those delicate perioral lines. It uses a resilient formula that moves naturally with your facial expressions. These are two different concerns in two different parts of the face, and each requires its own approach.","staff_close":"Jeuveau for upper-face expression lines, RHA Redensity as a finishing filler for perioral fine lines — two different zones requiring two different tools.","staff_talking_points":"When explaining this pairing: ''Jeuveau addresses the expression lines in the upper face — forehead, frown lines, crow''s feet — by relaxing the muscles that cause them. RHA Redensity addresses a completely different concern: those fine lines around the mouth. The perioral area moves constantly, so it needs a filler that can flex with those expressions, which is what RHA Redensity is designed to do.'' On Jeuveau: be straightforward that it''s an aesthetics-only neurotoxin made by Evolus. If patients ask how it compares to other options, the mechanism is the same and the provider can discuss individual fit. On RHA Redensity: ''It''s sometimes called a finishing filler because it handles the fine details after broader concerns like cheek volume and expression lines are addressed.'' These are different ecosystems (Evolus + Revance) — no shared loyalty program.","do_not_say":{"universal":["You need this","Everyone is doing this","This will make you look younger","Guaranteed results","Permanent","This will fix your problem","You''ll look natural","No one will know","This is painless","Zero downtime","Liquid facelift","This is our most popular package"],"pair_specific":["Jeuveau is better than Botox","RHA Redensity will erase all your lip lines","This will completely smooth the area around your mouth","You should do Jeuveau and RHA at every appointment"],"practice_specific":[]},"top_objections":[{"objection_type":"do_i_need_both","patient_says":"Can''t Jeuveau fix the lines around my mouth too?","handling_language":"Jeuveau addresses dynamic lines caused by muscle movement in specific areas — forehead, between the brows, crow''s feet. The fine lines around the mouth are a different type that develops from constant movement and skin changes over time. A neurotoxin in that area isn''t typically the right approach — that''s where a specialized filler like RHA Redensity comes in.","do_not_say_in_response":"You really need both. One without the other won''t work."},{"objection_type":"cost","patient_says":"This seems like a lot for different areas of my face.","handling_language":"These are genuinely different concerns in different parts of the face that require different tools. If you want to start with the concern that bothers you most, your provider can help you prioritize — they don''t need to happen at the same time.","do_not_say_in_response":"It''s worth doing everything at once to maximize results."},{"objection_type":"fear_of_overdone","patient_says":"I don''t want my mouth area to look stiff or overdone.","handling_language":"RHA Redensity is specifically designed for the perioral area because it needs to flex with natural movement. The goal is refined fine lines, not a frozen or stiff appearance. Your provider can discuss the amount and technique appropriate for your face.","do_not_say_in_response":"Don''t worry, it''ll look totally natural. No one will know."}],"sequencing_note":"Neurotoxin (Jeuveau) administered first, filler (RHA Redensity) second. If sequential visits: Jeuveau 2 weeks before RHA Redensity. In comprehensive multi-product plans: structural filler first, then neurotoxin, then RHA Redensity as final refinement step.","timing_note":"Same session or sequential visits. Jeuveau retreatment at 3-4 months. RHA Redensity perioral duration: per provider guidance based on individual results.","downtime_note":"Jeuveau: minimal — possible injection-site redness or bruising resolving within hours to a day. RHA Redensity (perioral): possible swelling, bruising, or tenderness in the perioral area.","same_session_ok":true,"maintenance_story":"Jeuveau every 3-4 months. RHA Redensity perioral: per provider guidance. Can schedule perioral refinement at a Jeuveau appointment when timing aligns.","rebooking_trigger":"At your 2-week Jeuveau follow-up, we can assess upper-face muscle response and check on the perioral area. Next Jeuveau appointment in 3-4 months.","next_visit_prompt":"How are the expression lines and the perioral area looking? We''ll plan your next Jeuveau appointment for 3-4 months from now.","source_support_summary":"PubMed DOI 10.1097/DSS.0000000000000754: BoNT-A and HA fillers may be performed together; combination superior to either alone (category-level). FDA label — Jeuveau: prabotulinumtoxinA-xvfs, aesthetics-only indication, Hi-Pure technology. FDA label — RHA Redensity: indicated for perioral area (superficial to mid dermis) for correction of dynamic perioral rhytids in adults over 22; resilient HA technology. Accepted clinical practice: neurotoxin-first sequencing.","evidence_level":"moderate","review_status":"pending","audience":"staff","patient_safe":true,"last_reviewed":null,"reviewed_by":null}'::jsonb,
